{
  "stem": "5228.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They didn't know this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "She was in such a dress that they didn't know that she is pregnant.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She got the baby in barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the SS woman-- she passed by there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And she heard the baby cry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And she came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "She took the baby.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And she stepped one feet, with her boots.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "With the other, she pulled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And she torn the baby to pieces.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And that's all of that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[CRYING] And they killed her, right away-- the mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they killed the baby-- both of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] we was there in Auschwitz [? not ?] long time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Then they took the-- one day, they-- the [NON-ENGLISH], the sister, from the woman what they got the baby there, she knew that we had the last transport to going out from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "This was already in '44, I think.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "She knew that we are going the last out from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I was lying, already, between the dead people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Well, I was so sick with diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I couldn't move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "I couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And she know I'm still alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "She took-- went there, and pulled me out, where I was lying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She talked to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And I-- I don't know if I know what she's saying, other than she begged me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Please, stay just how long they were counting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "Well, that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "What go-- get out from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "She beat me on both side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And she did like this to me, and of the hand, just-- just the-- that I feel in [? a ?] to staying how long they will count us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "OK, I was stand there, and everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "They count us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And they left-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And they put us in another barrack-- and not all of the girls.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
